137
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,850
Gelandangan tak berperasaan itu.

138
00:10:45,350 --> 00:10:46,480
Kamu bilang kamu ingin bernyanyi, bukan?

139
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,720
