201
00:16:00,700 --> 00:16:02,100
Kamu bukan tipe orang yang suka bercanda.

202
00:16:02,630 --> 00:16:03,730
Saya tidak bercanda.

203
00:16:04,740 --> 00:16:06,370
Maksudku, aku bisa mewujudkannya
jika kamu mau.

204
00:16:08,770 --> 00:16:09,770
Ada jalan.

205
00:16:14,380 --> 00:16:15,580
Dia tidak kerasukan.

206
00:16:20,780 --> 00:16:21,990
Itu benar-benar Kim Jin Ju.

207
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:29,860
Apa maksudmu?

208
00:16:33,100 --> 00:16:34,200
Bagaimana?

209
00:16:37,570 --> 00:16:38,640
Pertukaran otak.

210
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:49,810
Dia hanya terlihat seperti Momo. Hanya tubuhnya.

211
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:55,650
Pertama, ibu Momo, CEO Hyun.

212
00:16:56,690 --> 00:16:57,720
Dan kemudian Kim Jin Ju.

213
